Key Match Events: Mohammad Rizwan and Saud Shakeel hit identical half-centuries
Haris Rauf (3-43) finished the job by bowling out Paul van Meekeren
De Leede earlier ripped through the Pakistan line-up taking 4-62 and Colin Ackerman claimed 2-39
Miscellaneous Highlights: Pakistan made a winning start at the World Cup with an 81-run win over the Netherlands
The match was played at the Rajiv Gandhi International Cricket Stadium in Hyderabad
Pakistan kept chipping away to dismiss the underdogs for 205 in 41 overs
Others: The Dutch looked on course for a stunning win in Hyderabad at one stage as Vikramjit Singh (52) and Bas de Leede (67) got going
